Package HMS.Patient

Class Patient

java.lang.Object
HMS.User.User
HMS.Patient.Patient
public class Patient extends User
Represents a patient in the hospital management system, extending the User class with specific attributes for a patient's medical and personal information.

      contactNumber - The patient's contact phone number.
      emailAddress - The patient's email address.
      bloodType - The blood type of the patient.
      password - The patient's account password.
      loginCount - The number of times the patient has logged into the system.
